spanGrp.span: Ji s-kajki jera s-kajki rö je sũã'
I see that there are like many houses next to one another.
Yís të sũẽ bi-ra-nã tã'ĩ pe jũ tsõ blali rö yararbe (m) ña nã
I saw that a cat was looking at something inside something to see [binoculars].
yís të sũã'-ra-nã michi je të jirö sũẽ-gẽ-nã kã' sũẽ-gẽ jãrga nẽ
He is pretending to see something.
Je kayuwö-gẽ-nẽ-nã je të jirö sũẽ-gẽ-nẽ rö
We see that it looks like a bird locked in;
Se je të í sũẽ-ra rö dú yaba bi nẽ kajki-nẽ köte-lë-wã-nẽ
its owners keep locked inside something to lock in [a cage].
köte-lë-wã í wa í wakwa-wa jirö kötiö-glö jãrga
He is figuring out how to get in there to devour it, but he cannot devour it.
Je sũẽ-gẽ-ite-nã mẽnẽbi í köwã'u jeska je kötö-wã-nẽ-ra ka ĩã í katanã
When he manages to get in, a person puts him inside an old can that is lying there.
kö-gẽ-wã'u-ra í pe të í pakkáu-mĩ jele tarro biejo blali jãrga
He is pretending to see fire on his head.
Kayuwö-gẽ-nã í tsagu s/ í tsagu nã í të yugö wörkwa sũẽ-gẽ
So he came, passed by, and got up.
Jekepa jeska beteũ kau-mĩ-nẽ degãu-nẽ siwã' inga
We see that he was devouring/trying to devour a little bird;
Se je të í sũã'-ra dú yaba kajki-nẽ kete-gẽ-ite/ biá kete-wã-ite
It came out and passed by at once.
An old lady came by then;
she hit him on the head with a stick.
je të kal wa í kbá í tsagu inga
He pretended he had fallen down.
There he came back in and went back up once more.
jeska í jẽk pakká-ka-nẽ kagõu-nẽ siwã' inga etaba_gicha nẽ (hm)
We saw that there was a bird;
Se je të sũã-ra dú yaba bi kajki-nẽ
he kept on looking at it just figuring out whether to devour it or not.
je ki sũẽ-wã-ite-ra biá kete-wã-pa-ite wajebö í rö
But he could not devour it because it flew away from him.
Ka í katanã-wã ta ĩã jũr-gẽ í yiga
There he fell down and climbed up, as we can see, on a pipe.
Jeska í jánã-te-nẽ mẽnẽgau-nẽ se je të sũã-ra tubo bi jãrga nẽ
When he finally got up there, the fucking bird began to tease him;
Degãu-nẽ juei siwã' inga ska ra dú yaba bi chir-gẽ-nẽ í ra
brought a ball, put it in; it came out and went straight into his snout.
të mãga bola bi tsã'te pakká-wã-nẽ desãu-nẽ mõshanẽ kau-mĩ í ku jãrga-mĩ-nẽ
The asshole got to the road and flew away.
I don’t believe in that. It’s all a fucking lie.
ka je kuga-nã s-wã-nã jebi rö nẽ Í chir-gẽ kayuwö jela í rö
The ball remained in the fucking cat’s belly and flew down the road.
Taranã michi chi ñawã jãrga bola kachanãchá-nẽ jũr-gate ñala wa
That’s how I saw it. There it ended.’
Jebi bö yís sũã' jeska í onã'-wã
